net.stemkoski.bagel

Class Input

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.stemkoski.bagel.Input

  • public class Input
extends java.lang.Object
    A structure for storing and updating the state of hardware input devices (keyboard and mouse). Handles key down/press/up events, mouse down/up events, and mouse position.
